content.rendered:
Directed by Akarsh Khurana

Written by Adhir Bhat

Cast Sumeet Vyas (Rakesh). Mantra Mugdh (Vinit (Hijacker 3)). Sonnalli Seygall (Dilshaad (as Sonalli Sehgal)) . Boloram Das (IpadMan). Nipun Dharmadhikari (ATC Senior Official). Sarthak Kakar (Nakul (Hijacker 1)). Mohammad Salman Khan (Salman). Adhaar Khurana (Pilot (Male)). Gaurav Mankoti (Dancer 3).Abish Mathew. Kumud Mishra (Mr. Taneja). Yusof Mutahar (Gourav). Priyanshu Painyuli (Chaitanya (Cricketer)). Muzamil Qureshi (Taikom (Hijacker 4)). Taaruk Raina (Parth (Nerd guy)). Vikash Rajput (Vikash Rajput). Natasha Rastogi (Mrs. Taneja). Sarang Sathaye (Dheeraj (Hijacker 2) (as Sarang Sathye)). Faiyaz Shaikh (CISF Officer). Chaitnya Sharma (Amanda / Amitosh). Chandni Srivastava (Dancer 1). Akash Thapa (Ningthouja Manipuri Man). Amey Wagh (ATC Junior Official)

Language Hindi

Producers Vivek b Agrawal. Vikas Bahl. Tanvi Gandhi. Nickhil Jakatdar. Madhu Mantena Varma. Vikramaditya Motwane. Arun Prakash. Ranjan Singh

Production Phantom Film
